    "Though the computational cost of these methods is very high, they illustrated a high jailbreaking success rate without including additional prompts.",
    "presented a systematic benchmark for 13 state-of-the-art jailbreaking attacks of different approaches on several most popular LLMs [40].",
    "Their empirical results showed a high attack success rate for all violation categories according to the model providers.",
    "Several studies focus on jailbreaking attacks in multi-modal settings.",
